profile:
Two Small Men With Big Hearts Moving is one of Canada's largest network of independent moving companies . Our goal is to provide a top level of moving service anywhere in Canada at a competitive price. This will ensure stable, steady growth and make us a force in the future.  We offer local and long distance moving services for homes, apartments & offices within Canada.

profile:
Professional Moving Canada provides residential and commercial moving services for people relocating or need help moving items within their home. 

We offer local and long distance moving services for are clients. Every-time you use professional moving Canada we make sure you are looked after and feel good once everything is done. 

Our positive attitude on life and business allows our clients to be stress free and comfortable throughout the whole process. 

It is preferred to set up a free consultation for us to see what we will be moving and meet with our clients. 

We are based out of London Ontario and service surrounding areas, we have a secondary office in Windsor Ontario. 

Website: www.professionalmoving.ca

Email: professionalmovingcanada@gmail.com

Phone Number: 519-878-5804
